title.narrative: Delivery Team Top Up (DTTU) Operations - Crown Agents

description.narrative: This activity (Delivery Team Top Up (DTTU) Operations - Crown Agents) is a component of Sexual and Reproductive Health and HIV Prevention in Zimbabwe reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,939,827. This component benefits Zimbabwe, and works in the following sector(s): Reproductive health care, Family planning, STD control including HIV/AIDS. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-08-2012 and the end date is 31-12-2016.
